data: The event Project Alpha Review was held to conduct a milestone review and status update for Project Alpha.
The event Project Alpha Review content included a discussion that API version changes caused minor delays in the integration phase.
The event Project Alpha Review content included a proposal to extend the project timeline by one week to accommodate the integration delays.
The event Project Alpha Review concluded with the decision to extend the timeline by one week and to allocate additional resources if needed.
The event Project Alpha Review included the approval of budget implications by finance and the update of the project risk log.
The event Project Alpha Review identified next steps to finalize the test plan and schedule the UAT environment.
